reviewText: Best anime ever!!!  Definately get it with subtitles. English version takes so much away

HERE IT IS, KILL LA KILL, THE ENTIRE SERIES!! YAY!! YIPPEEE!!! Okay, let me calm down here. I ordered this under the impression that I could get it for WAAAAY cheaper than what these other guys are selling theirs for, and I was RIGHT!!! For $29.99, I got THE ENTIRE SERIES, EXCEPT for THE LAST CHAPTER (25). I figure I could get it somewhere down the line, it's on a Anime app where you can watch it, so all is not lost. BUT, this is THE BARGAIN OF THE CENTURY, for anyone wanting this SWEET SERIES!!! It's in Japanese and a couple of other foreign languages, but has English subtitles. WELL WORTH IT!!! Thank You TeddySmiles!!!
